{"name":"Word Of Pain","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You speak one of the secret names of the Chaos Gods. Simply annunciating this word causes those around you incredible pain. Centre the large template on yourself. Those affected take a Damage 8 hit that ignores armour, but not toughness bonus, and must make a successful Will Power Test or become helpless for 1 round. You are not affected by word of pain.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Dark Lore (Chaos)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":"8"},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":27},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"The blood of a Daemon","bonus":3},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"1NblsuucbguH1eb0"}
{"name":"Burning Blood","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You spit blood that burns like acid at any one target within 24 yards (12 squares). The target suffers a number of Damage 4 hits equal to your Magic Characteristic. This is a magic missile.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Dark Lore (Chaos)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"24"},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":"4"},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":13},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A vial of Daemon blood","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"5tuStIMvbIXJqyJb"}
{"name":"Vision Of Torment","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You cause any one character within 24 yards (12 squares) to have a hellish vision. The target is stunned for 1 round unless a successful Will Power Test is made. Once the character recovers from being stunned, he must make a second Will Power Test or gain 1 Insanity Point.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Dark Lore (Chaos)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":7},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A small mask","bonus":1},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"6eVY5lt3ZJQfjbfb"}
{"name":"Lure Of Chaos","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You ensorcell one character with 24 yards (12 squares) and bend him to your will. Unless the target makes a successful Will Power Test, you decide what actions he takes on his next turn. Undead are immune to the lure of Chaos.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Dark Lore (Chaos)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"24"},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":16},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A defiled holy symbol","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"9rekfFPnf8UrFtzZ"}
{"name":"Dark Hand Of Destruction","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You wreath your hand in a nimbus of dark magic. It counts as a magic weapon with the Armour Piercing Quality and Damage 7 and you gain a +10% bonus to your Weapon Skill when attacking with it. The spell remains in effect for a number of rounds equal to your Magic Characteristic. You can retain it with a successful Will Power Test each round thereafter.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Dark Lore (Chaos)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":17},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Full Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"The hand of a hanged man","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"Q9xr3E411H77BFVL"}
{"name":"Touch Of Chaos","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Your touch channels pure Chaos energy into one target, causing him to mutate and change unless a successful Will Power Test is made. If the test is failed the target must roll on Table 11-1: Chaos Mutations. The mutation manifests in a matter of seconds and is permanent. If affected the target must also make a successful Will Power Test or be stunned for 1 round by the suddenness and vileness of the change. This is a touch spell. Undead are immune to the touch of Chaos.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Dark Lore (Chaos)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":20},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"The horn of a Beastman","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"UcXQlKwmK2jnyuF9"}
{"name":"Veil Of Corruption","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You create a foul cloud of corruption anywhere within 36 yards (18 squares). Use the large template. Those affected must make a Will Power Test or lose 1 Wound regardless of Toughness Bonus or armour. Wounded characters continue to lose 1 wound per round until a successful Will Power Test is made. Those who suffer more than 1 Wound must also make a Toughness Test or begin to mutate. Those who fail the test gain a Chaos Mutation; roll on Table 11-1: Chaos Mutations on page 229 to generate the mutations.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Dark Lore (Chaos)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"36"},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":24},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Full Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"The blade of a Chaos Champion","bonus":3},"template":{"value":"large"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"fRod2xl7HB2Vp9St"}
{"name":"Boon Of Chaos","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You call upon the favour of the dark Gods of Chaos. You gain a +10% bonus to Weapon Skill, Toughness, Will Power, or Fellowship for 1 minute (6 rounds).</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Dark Lore (Chaos)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":9},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Full Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"An amulet engraved with the symbol of one of the Gods of Chaos","bonus":1},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"jZkPVfVPUGCW14gu"}
{"name":"Summon Lesser Daemon","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You summon one Lesser Daemon, which appears in any unoccupied spot within 12 yards (6 squares) of you. The Daemon remains for 1d10 minutes.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Dark Lore (Chaos)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":12},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"2 Full Actions"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"The fresh heart of a humanoid","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"kW7538OP8YbMuPAt"}
{"name":"Summon Daemon Pack","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You summon a number of Lesser Daemons equal to your Magic Characteristic. They appear in any unoccupied spots within 12 yards (6 squares) of you and remain for 1d10 minutes.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Dark Lore (Chaos)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":25},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"2 Full Actions"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"The fresh hearts of six humanoids","bonus":3},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"ySVZiMSkgeVW1WhX"}
